 1. Recycler View :-
  - View Group
  - Cells can be re-generated when hide from user's vision and recycled.
  - Aquire less space when compare to List and GridView .



   Needs :-
   - Activity
   - Adapter extends to RecyclerView.Adapter with ViewHolder
   - ModelClass











